#!/bin/bash

cat <<EOF
This is an AsciiBinder documentation builder image.

For more information on AsciiBinder, see the documentation: 
http://www.asciibinder.org/latest/welcome/

To use it, install S2I: https://github.com/openshift/source-to-image

Sample invocation:

s2i build https://github.com/openshift/openshift-docs.git openshift-s2i/asciibinder-018-centos7 openshift-docs

You can then run the resulting image via:
docker run -p 8080:8080 openshift-docs
EOF
